    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Code node\nIt's the transformation layer between the raw LLM response and the file that gets written to Drive.\n1. Catches LLM failures. If the LLM node errores, it writes an error report instead of crashing the pipeline (this error .txt gets then uploaded in Drive.\n2. Extracts the summary text from the LLM response.\n3. Builds the output. Formats the summary with a timestamp header and generates a unique filename.",
