      "parameters": {
        "content": "## What this Workflow does\n\n- It's a fully automated file processing pipeline. File in, summary out, no manual steps.\n- Two layers of error handling that do different jobs. Soft failure writes an error file uploaded to Drive, hard crash alerts you on Discord using another workflow called Error Handler.\n- Proper credentials management with no hardcoded keys anywhere. ",
